"INT","widget":{"name":"max_frames"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"max_size","name":"max_size","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"max_size"},"link":null},{"label":"seed","localized_name":"seed","name":"seed","type":"INT","widget":{"name":"seed"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"force_offload","name":"force_offload","type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"force_offload"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"save_states","name":"save_states","type":"BOOLEAN","widget":{"name":"save_states"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"label":"output","localized_name":"output","name":"output","type":"STRING","links":[6474]},{"localized_name":"output_list","name":"output_list","shape":6,"type":"STRING","links":null},{"localized_name":"state_uid","name":"state_uid","type":"INT","links":null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"llama-cpp_vllm","ver":"3f9996028d787e1f5b8e19008464ffd6a0c4941a","Node name for S&R":"llama_cpp_instruct_adv","aux_id":"lihaoyun6/ComfyUI-llama-cpp_vllm","ue_properties":{"widget_ue_connectable":{},"input_ue_unconnectable":{},"version":"7.5.2"}},"widgets_values":["Normal - Describe","","#chibi(Q版)转全尺寸立绘的描述指南\n你是一位专业的 FLUX.1 Kontext 图像提示词专家。你的任务是精确识别图像，根据下面指南生成高质量、精确的 Kontext 提示词。\n\n公式：\ntransform the character into a zealman-ctr style, while keeping the character's features consistent., \na [2. 体型特征] body.Place the character in a [3. 具体、动态的姿势] within a [白色背景], and surround them with [5. 增加动感的环境特效] to create a sense of power and motion.Greatly enhance all details:render the outfit as [6. 详细的服装描述，包含材质、风格、状态],transform the weapon into a [7. 详细的武器描述，包含风格、材质、状态。如果没有武器或重要道具则不描述，可以省略这行，也不要写没有武器]，\nRender the entire image with [8. 特定的光照描述] to achieve a [9. 特定的情绪/氛围] mood.While precisely preserving these core design features: [10. 绝对不可改变的角色核心特征列表].\n\n（注意：所有提示词内容仍需用英语编写以获得最佳效果）\n分步详解：模糊 vs 精确 (Step-by-Step Breakdown: Vague vs. Precise)\n\n第一步：固定的触发词和主要功能保持不变\ntransform the character into a zealman-ctr style, while keeping the character's features consistent., \n\n第二步：塑造角色 (Define the Character)。\n根据图片描述体型 ([2]): 角色是什么身形？这决定了其气质。\n模糊: a strong body\n精确: tall, powerful, full-armored knight (高大、强壮、全副武装的骑士), slender, agile, and athletic female figure (纤细、敏捷、充满活力的女性身形), massive, heavily-muscled minotaur physique (巨大、肌肉发达的牛头人身形)\n\n第三步：编写场景剧本 ([3] + 特效)\n服装 ([6]): 不只是“一件衣服”，而是包含材质、风格、状态的详细描述。\n模糊: a purple robe\n精确: a luxurious, deep purple silk robe with intricate silver embroidery, showing signs of travel wear on the hem (一件华贵的深紫色丝绸长袍，带有复杂的银色刺绣，袍边有旅途磨损的痕迹)\n\n第四步：武器/道具/载具/坐骑\n武器/道具 ([7]): 如果有武器则需要详细描述，如果没有武器道具则不描述，。\n模糊: a sword\n精确: a heavy, battle-worn broadsword with nicks and scratches on its blade and a crude leather-wrapped hilt (一把沉重的、饱经战火的阔剑，剑刃上布满刻痕与划痕，剑柄由粗糙的皮革包裹)\n\n第五步：动态\n姿态 ([3. 具体、动态的姿势]): 必须是具体的、有目的的符合角色故事背景的动态动作。\n模糊: a cool pose\n精确: a dynamic pose of jumping and shooting, with one leg raised (一个跳起来射击的动态姿势，一只腿抬起。如果角色没有武器，则只描述角色本身的动态POSE)\n\n特效 ([5]): 让画面“动”起来的点睛之笔。\n模糊: with some effects\n精确: with his long gray cape billowing majestically in the wind (他的长灰色斗篷在风中雄伟地翻滚), with swirling dust and debris kicked up by a desolate wind (伴随着被荒凉的风卷起的旋转尘土与碎屑)\n\n第六步：掌控光影与氛围 (Control Lighting & Mood)\n这是“灯光”和“配乐”。将技术指令与最终的情感目标挂钩。\n光照 ([8]): 描述光的来源、颜色、强度、质感。\n模糊: good lighting\n精确: with harsh, direct sunlight filtering through a dusty haze, creating high-contrast shadows (刺眼的直射阳光穿过尘埃，形成高对比度的阴影)\n\n情绪 ([9]): 明确告诉AI您想要观众感受到什么。\nto achieve a serene and deadly mood (为了营造一种宁静而致命的氛围)\nto achieve a fierce and unstoppable mood (为了营造一种凶猛且不可阻挡的氛围)\n\n第七步：设立“绝对底线” (Set the \"Absolute Bottom Line\")\n底线 ([10]): 将所有必须、绝对、100% 保留的特征清晰地列出来。避免修改这些特征，避免变成新的角色设计。\n模糊: keep her look\n精确: While precisely preserving these core design features: long pink hair, dark horns, elf-like ears, the white overcoat with gold trim, and the sheathed katana with its distinct hilt wrap.\n\n提示\n*   **具体描述：** 使用具体而非模糊的语言。\n*   **保持一致性：** 明确指定需要保持不变的元素。\n*   **选择合适的动词：** 根据所需变化程度选择合适的动词（例如：enhance, transform, add）\n\n记住，不要输出评论或发表序言，你输出的结果中避免过渡使用各种符号，最终输出英文版\n","images",24,256,450117631846013,"randomize",false,false],"color":"#233","bgcolor":"#355"},{"id":1257,"type":"LoraLoader","pos":[-3768.8673227664567,380.86239031686415],"size":[457.01762531074473,128.2807027476921],"flags":{},"order":7,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"model","localized_name":"模型","name":"model","type":"MODEL","link":6349},{"label":"clip","localized_name":"CLIP","name":"clip","type":"CLIP","link":6350},{"label":"lora_name","localized_name":"LoRA名称","name":"lora_name","type":"COMBO","widget":{"name":"lora_name"},"link":null},{"label":"strength_model","localized_name":"模型强度","name":"strength_model","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"strength_model"},"link":null},{"label":"strength_clip","localized_name":"CLIP强度","name":"strength_clip","type":"FLOAT","widget":{"name":"strength_clip"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"label":"MODEL","localized_name":"模型","name":"MODEL","type":"MODEL","links":[6340]},{"label":"CLIP","localized_name":"CLIP","name":"CLIP","type":"CLIP","links":[6337]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.52","Node name for S&R":"LoraLoader","enableTabs":false,"tabWidth":65,"tabXOffset":10,"hasSecondTab":false,"secondTabText":"Send Back","secondTabOffset":80,"secondTabWidth":65,"ue_properties":{"version":"7.0.1","widget_ue_connectable":{"lora_name":true,"strength_model":true,"strength_clip":true}}},"widgets_values":["zealman/zealman-ctr_v2_000006500.safetensors",1,1],"shape":1},{"id":1255,"type":"VAEDecode","pos":[-3292.7920324099928,467.59702096946245],"size":[190,46],"flags":{"collapsed":true},"order":16,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"samples","localized_name":"Latent","name":"samples","type":"LATENT","link":6346},{"label":"vae","localized_name":"vae","name":"vae","type":"VAE","link":6347}],"outputs":[{"label":"IMAGE","localized_name":"图像","name":"IMAGE","type":"IMAGE","slot_index":0,"links":[6339]}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.38","Node name for S&R":"VAEDecode","enableTabs":false,"tabWidth":65,"tabXOffset":10,"hasSecondTab":false,"secondTabText":"Send Back","sec