into a massive, oversized heavy cannon. Render it with a matte black and dark grey metallic finish, covered in intricate paneling and mechanical details. The cannon must feature numerous glowing red energy conduits running along its length, culminating in a large, brightly glowing red muzzle. The weapon should look incredibly powerful and heavy, yet she wields it with practiced ease.\nRender the entire image in a polished, painterly style with dramatic, cinematic lighting. Use the glowing red parts of the cannon to cast strong red light and reflections onto her body, hair, and gear. The mood should be energetic, powerful, and a bit rebellious or cocky.\nWhile precisely preserving these core design features: the long, spiky blonde hair with an ahoge, the blue eyes, the tech-goggles on her forehead, the black outfit with red and gold accents, the specific design of the massive heavy cannon, and the gold belt buckle with its red sash."],"color":"#232","bgcolor":"hsla(120, 25%, 26.7%, 1)","shape":1},{"id":1252,"type":"SaveImage","pos":[-3768.59130859375,545.5013427734375],"size":[456.8831481933594,751.605712890625],"flags":{"collapsed":false},"order":17,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"images","localized_name":"图片","name":"images","type":"IMAGE","link":6339},{"label":"filename_prefix","localized_name":"文件名前缀","name":"filename_prefix","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"filename_prefix"},"link":null}],"outputs":[],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfy-core","ver":"0.3.44","Node name for S&R":"SaveImage","enableTabs":false,"tabWidth":65,"tabXOffset":10,"hasSecondTab":false,"secondTabText":"Send Back","secondTabOffset":80,"secondTabWidth":65,"ue_properties":{"version":"7.0.1","widget_ue_connectable":{}}},"widgets_values":["%date:yyyyMMdd%/image_"],"shape":1},{"id":1325,"type":"llama_cpp_model_loader","pos":[-3276.7379562907954,625.2248220834786],"size":[272.087890625,202],"flags":{},"order":4,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"label":"model","localized_name":"model","name":"model","type":"COMBO","wid